     Vallourec Live!

Vallourec Live!

   ​​​31/10/2016 - Vallourec has been rated A- by CDP (Carbon Disclosure
   Project) in its 2016 Global Climate Change Report. This worldwide
   reference program tracks and rates corporate actions to reduce
   greenhouse gas emissions. It’s our 7th participation and our best
   score!
   Read the report
